title: Metal Mulisha Exhaust - Jeep JK by Gibson Performance
description:
Metal Mulisha Exhaust by Gibson Performance hits the market hard with all new sound and style for Jeep JK owners, '07-present 2 & 4 door models.  Each Black Ceramic coated system bumps up the decibels with a throaty tone, and features Metal Mulisha Stainless Steel Skull badges wrapped around HUGE dual 5" rear-exit exhaust tips! All Metal Mulisha Exhaust exhaust systems are manufactured for hassle-free installation, Made in the U.S.A, and finished with Gibson Performance's commitment to their customer by including a Lifetime Limited Warranty. 

Brian Deegan, Metal Mulisha's founder and decorated X-Games & multi-talented racing champion commented, "The Metal Mulisha Exhaust brings the motor to life and makes it fun to drive! That's why all my vehicles and race trucks run the Metal Mulisha Exhaust!" 

Part #60-0023
- '07-'11 3.8L Jeep JK 2/4 Door
- 2012  3.6L Jeep JK 2/4 Door
